metadata.name: Morning walk
metadata.description:
Early in the morning when I took this photo. I was fined 30 euros by the police.
But it was worth it.
Builders called the police,they were doing renovations in the house next door,and when they saw a naked girl, they immediately called the police.
Even though it was beautiful.
I am satisfied with the shooting, and no one else will take such a shot!
